  "notes": [
    "Source: IRremoteESP8266 (github.com/crankyoldgit/IRremoteESP8266) — ir_LG.h/.cpp, MIT license.",
    "Remote model: LG6711A20083V.  Korean lineup: TS-H122ERM1 등 2010~2013년 모델.",
    "LG (28-bit) — SwingV는 단일 토글 명령만 사용.",
    "All state commands are computed for the model's fan-code scheme using IRremoteESP8266's encoder. mode_*, temp_*, fan_* defaults: COOL mode @ 24°C with fan-auto.",
    "Toggle/sub commands (power_off, light_toggle, swing_v_*) are literal IRremoteESP8266 constants and identical across LG2 models.",
    "Horizontal swing not supported by this remote.",
    "power_on sends the standard COOL/24°C/auto state packet — modern LG ACs treat any state with Power=ON as a power-on command.",
    "All commands round-trip with the firmware decoder; for non-default state combinations, send the raw computed code from the encoder or capture via learn flow.",
    "Carrier: 38 kHz."
